                    </h4>
                    <p className="text-rose-100/80 text-sm">Aproveite todas as ferramentas premium antes da expiração.</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <button onClick={() => setActiveTab('paywall')} className="px-8 py-3 bg-white text-rose-900 rounded-xl font-black text-sm hover:scale-105 active:scale-95 transition-all shadow-lg">
                  Assinar Agora
